48、Herbert George Wells威爾斯1866-1946 科幻小說：The Time Machine時間機器;The Island of Dr Morau莫洛博士島;The Invisible Man隱身人;When the Sleeper Waked;The Shape of Things to Come未來事物的面貌 An Outline of World Histrory 世界史綱社會生活小說：Tono Bungay托諾·班格;Ann Veronica安·維羅尼卡;Kipps基普斯
49、 Enoch Arnord Bennett阿諾德·本涅特1867-1931 A Man from the North北方人;Anna of the Five Towns五鎮上的安娜;The Old Wives’ Tale老婦譚;Clayhanger克萊亨厄劇本：Milestones;How to Live Twentyfour Hours a Day
50、 John Galworthy高爾斯華綏1867-1933 From the Four Winds天涯海角(The Man of Property有產業的人;In Chancery騎虎難下;To Let出租→The Forsyte Saga福爾塞世家);(The White Monkey白猿;The Silver Spoon銀匙;Swan Song天鵝曲→A Modern Comedy現代喜劇)劇作：The Silver Box銀匣;Strife鬥爭
51、Saki薩奇（Hector Hugh Munro孟柔）1870-1916 短篇小說集：Reginald雷金納德;Reginald in Russia;The Chronicles of Clovis克洛維斯記事;Beats and Super-beats;The Toys of Peace;The Square Egg方蛋名文：Dusk
52、Edward Morgan Forster福斯特1879-1970 長篇小說：Where Angels Fear to Tread天使們忘而卻步的地方;The Longest Journey最漫長的旅程;A Room with a View可以遠眺的地方;A Passage to India印度之行短篇小說集：The Eternal Moment永恆的時刻散文集：Abinger Harvest在阿賓格村的收穫;Two Cheers for Democracy
53、 John Millington Synge沁孤1871-1909 The Playboy of the Western World西方世界的花花公子;Riders to the Sea騎馬下海的人們;Deridre of Sorrows悲傷的黛達爾;In the Shade of the Glen在幽谷的陰影下;The Tinker’s Wedding補鍋匠的婚禮
