56、John Masefield梅斯菲爾德1878-1967 詩：Salt-Water Ballads海上歌謠;The Everlasting Mercy永久的仁慈;The Widow in the Bye Street小街的寡婦;The Daffodil Fields水仙田;Reynard the Fox狐狸雷納德小說：Captain Margaret;Multitude and Solitude群與獨;Sard Harker薩德·哈克爾劇本：The Locked Chest
