58、 Sean O’casey肖恩·奧凱西1880-1964 劇本：The Shadow of a Gunman槍手的影子;Juno and the Peacock裘諾與孔雀;The Plough and the Stars犁與星;The Star Turns Red;Red Roses for Me給我紅玫瑰自傳體小說：I Knock at the Door我敲門;Pictures in the Hallway門廳裏的圖畫;Drums under Windows窗下鼓聲;Inishfallen,Fare Thee Well英尼希法倫，再見;Rose and Crown;Sunset and Evening Star日落與金星
